{"tid":1859398,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"強尼戴普家暴案「大翻盤」 網氣喊：梅拉公主從水行俠滾蛋","createTime":"2020-02-03T08:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T11:44:35.000Z","uid":38539,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd4eb07752c8531653ed4d50e18a4c69582f723","tid":1859398,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:30:48.000Z","msg":"好萊塢男星強尼戴普（Johnny Depp）與前妻安柏赫德（Amber Heard）的家暴案鬧得沸沸揚揚，儘管兩人已經離婚，不過依然互相指責對方有「家暴情形」，強叔被指控打人﹑酗酒還家暴，讓安柏赫德身心俱疲，不過在最近的消息指出，一則兩人對話的錄音黨曝光，裏頭安柏赫德認了有打人，讓整個案情翻盤，目前也有網友開始向華納連署，要安柏赫德退出《水行俠2》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://c-7npsfqifvt0x24jnh-t-nto-dpnx2eblbnbjafex2eofu.g01.msn.com/g00/3_c-7x78x78x78.nto.dpn_/c-7NPSFQIFVT0x24iuuqtx3ax2fx2fjnh-t-nto-dpn.blbnbjafe.ofux2fufoboux2fbnqx2ffoujuzjex2fCCABvrw.jnhx3fix3d511x26x78x3d392x26nx3d7x26rx3d71x26px3dgx26mx3dgx26yx3d307x26zx3d449x26j21d.nbslx3djnbhf_$/$/$/$/$\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc-7npsfqifvt0x24jnh-t-nto-dpnx2eblbnbjafex2eofu.g01.msn.com%2Fg00%2F3_c-7x78x78x78.nto.dpn_%2Fc-7NPSFQIFVT0x24iuuqtx3ax2fx2fjnh-t-nto-dpn.blbnbjafe.ofux2fufoboux2fbnqx2ffoujuzjex2fCCABvrw.jnhx3fix3d511x26x78x3d392x26nx3d7x26rx3d71x26px3dgx26mx3dgx26yx3d307x26zx3d449x26j21d.nbslx3djnbhf_%24%2F%24%2F%24%2F%24%2F%24&h=cabe6428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&copy; 由 三立新聞網 提供<br />\n▲強尼戴普近年來深受家務事影響（圖／翻攝自imdb、theblast ）<br />\n<br />\n安柏赫德在DC影業的英雄電影《水行俠》中飾演身材姣好的「梅拉公主」，性感卻又不失帥氣的模樣在全球引發討論，然而她與強尼戴普的婚姻卻比電影還精彩，儘管口口聲聲指控強尼戴普打人，但根據《每日郵報》透露，錄音黨中她卻親口承認有丟花瓶跟鍋子等等的留言，甚至還表示這樣不是揍人，只是打人，引發外界一陣譁然。<br />\n<img src=\"https://c-7npsfqifvt0x24jnh-t-nto-dpnx2eblbnbjafex2eofu.g01.msn.com/g00/3_c-7x78x78x78.nto.dpn_/c-7NPSFQIFVT0x24iuuqtx3ax2fx2fjnh-t-nto-dpn.blbnbjafe.ofux2fufoboux2fbnqx2ffoujuzjex2fBBIlcRT.jnhx3fix3d621x26x78x3d621x26nx3d7x26rx3d71x26px3dgx26mx3dgx26yx3d329x26zx3d272x26j21d.nbslx3djnbhf_$/$/$/$/$\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc-7npsfqifvt0x24jnh-t-nto-dpnx2eblbnbjafex2eofu.g01.msn.com%2Fg00%2F3_c-7x78x78x78.nto.dpn_%2Fc-7NPSFQIFVT